headline.main: South Korea to Ban Imports of U.S. Poultry as Bird Flu Found in U.S.
headline.print_headline: South Korea to Ban Imports of U.S. Poultry as Bird Flu Found in U.S.

lead_paragraph: South Korea will ban imports of U.S. poultry after a strain of H7 bird flu virus was confirmed at a U.S. chicken farm, the agriculture ministry said on Monday.
